      "content": "but therapy doesn't change what i am. it's just a way to delay the inevitable. they're always so stressed because of me, always walking on eggshells. don't you see? if i weren't around, that pressure would just... disappear. they could actually breathe. it's almost like the most loving thing i could do is just remove the source of their stress.",
